<p>
<b>Hint</b>: It is also possible to search in a project without needing to open a
file beforehand. To do so use <code>SPC p p</code> and then <code>C-s</code> on a given project to
directly search into it like with <code>SPC s p</code>.
</p>
</div>
</li>

<li><a id="sec-14-7-1-6" name="sec-14-7-1-6"></a>Searching the web<br  /><div class="outline-text-5" id="text-14-7-1-6">
