<td class="left">unwrap current expression and kill all symbols after point</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="left"><code>SPC k E</code></td>
<td class="left">unwrap current expression and kill all symbols before point</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="left"><code>SPC k h</code></td>
